A '''quulaar''' was a piece of clothing used by [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]] to carry heavy loads and [[Youngling/Legends|younglings]] who were not yet old enough to climb on their own. The name literally meant "baby-sack". [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Jarik Solo]] were once carried in them during a visit to [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]].

